Package container

Class RegistrationList

java.lang.Object
container.RegistrationList
public class RegistrationList extends Object
Manages all officer registration records for BTO projects in the system.

Supports loading from and saving to CSV, and provides methods to add, remove, and query registrations based on officer or project.
